Revision history for Getopt-Long-Bash

0.7.1 2026-01-17T02:19:55Z

    - Fix callback function naming for hyphenated options (list-themes calls list_themes)

0.7.0 2025-12-30T12:52:21Z

    - Fix passthru negation with short option aliases (--no-v was becoming -v)

0.6.0 2025-12-24T07:22:23Z

    - Allow whitespace around mark character keys for alignment
    - Improve documentation with clearer examples
    - Update Tutorial with spaced option definition format

0.5.0 2025-12-23T12:10:40Z

    - Initial CPAN release
    - Bash library for Getopt::Long-like option parsing
